{{#if usesHexagonalArchitecture}}
### Hexagonal Architecture (Ports & Adapters)

**Non-negotiable rule:** each service's domain defines ports (interfaces). Infrastructure implements adapters. No use-case imports infrastructure SDKs directly.

```
domain/
  entities/        # Pure domain entities
  ports/           # Interfaces (IMessagePublisher, IRepository, etc.)
  use-cases/       # Business logic — depends only on ports

application/       # Orchestrates use-cases

infrastructure/
  messaging/       # Messaging adapters
  persistence/     # Persistence adapters
```
{{/if}}

